    "text": "Ishmail De Niro is an artist, printmaker & artist-curator based between\nBirmingham & London. Co-Founder & Co-Director of Prayer Room, De Niro\nworks across printmaking, curation and sculpture to articulate an aesthetic\nof heritage, disenfranchisement & care. His charged works employ indus-\ntrial materials, print (screen) and faith spaces with a focus on the “irl” to\nproduce distinctive experiences. De Niro’s work is a study that aligns his\nambition to make and understand through his current experimentation he\nphrases as ‘Artist working it out’.",
